                                                              C. 6/8 Aug 65
Dear Frederic

.ue 2
                                                                       $.#$
Forts.: 6/8 Aug 65
With much love to Mama tell her please that till now we have no prei·elbern
as soon as we get some I will look about the price, tell her also that the
butter costs 33 Creuzer so of course I buy none for her.

We are to go to Kalmbach Marie, Ettle and myself with Miss Seger and I have
but little time. Give my love to David. I am glad you got trawsers and west
from Onkel G please to thank him in my name.

                        With love yours J. Gundert


